font-extrabold text-[var(--color-navy)] mb-6 tracking-tight\">Contact <span class=\"text-[var(--color-primary)]\">Us</span></h1><p class=\"text-gray-500 max-w-xl mx-auto text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed\">Have a project in mind, need technical assistance, or just want to say hello? Get in touch with our team of digital experts.</p></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-16 z-0\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(to top, #ffffff, transparent)\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div></section><section class=\"max-w-[1320px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-8 mb-20\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col justify-between gap-8\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\"><div class=\"w-8 h-[2px] bg-[var(--color-primary)]\"></div><span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-[var(--color-primary)] tracking-widest uppercase\">Reach Out</span></div><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-navy)] leading-tight mb-6\">Our Office &amp; <span class=\"text-[var(--color-secondary)]\">Info</span></h2><p class=\"text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-8\">Stop by our office for a cup of coffee, or drop us an email anytime. We usually respond within 24 business hours.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-[var(--shadow-card)] hover:border-[var(--color-primary)] transition-all\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-phone\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M13.832 16.568a1 1 0 0 0 1.213-.303l.355-.465A2 2 0 0 1 17 15h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2A18 18 0 0 1 2 4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-.8 1.6l-.468.351a1 1 0 0 0-.292 1.233 14 14 0 0 0 6.392 6.384\"></path></svg></div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] mb-1\">Call Us</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1\">Mon-Sat, 10am-6pm</p><a href=\"tel:+919519498159\" class=\"text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline\">+91 9519498159</a></div><div class=\"bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-[var(--shadow-card)] hover:border-[var(--color-secondary)] transition-all\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m22 7-8.991 5.727a2 2 0 0 1-2.009 0L2 7\"></path><rect x=\"2\" y=\"4\" width=\"20\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg></div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] mb-1\">Email Us</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1\">Drop a message anytime</p><a href=\"mailto:info@jugaduji.com\" class=\"text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-secondary)] hover:underline\">info@jugaduji.com</a></div><div class=\"bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-[var(--shadow-card)] hover:border-[var(--color-accent)] transition-all sm:col-span-2\"><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-orange-50 text-orange-500 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] mb-1\">Visit Our Office</h4><p class=\"text-xs sm:text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Front Of Hotel The Grand, Civil Line Road, Robertsganj, Uttar Pradesh, India</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-[var(--color-blue-gradient)]/40 border border-blue-100/50 p-5 rounded-2xl flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock text-[var(--color-primary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg></div><p class=\"text-xs sm:text-sm text-[var(--color-navy)] font-medium leading-relaxed\">Need a rapid response? Click the floating WhatsApp button in the corner to speak with an agent instantly!</p></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-7\"><div class=\"bg-white p-6 sm:p-10 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-[var(--shadow-lg)]\"><h3 class=\"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] mb-6 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-square text-[var(--color-primary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M22 17a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6.828a2 2 0 0 0-1.414.586l-2.202 2.202A.71.71 0 0 1 2 21.286V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z\"></path></svg>Send a Message</h3><form class=\"space-y-5\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5\"><div><label for=\"name\" class=\"block text-xs font-bold text-[var(--color-navy)] uppercase tracking-wider mb-2\">Your Name</label><input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-sm t